media:group.media:title: Children Can Get Fentanyl Easily (SHOCKING)
media:group.media:description:
Fentanyl is now the leading cause of death for young Americans between the ages of 18-45. Adam Gordon, Assistant U.S. Attorney in the Southern District of California, sits with PragerU CEO Marissa Streit to explain why Fentanyl is so lethal and what parents can do to protect their children.

Watch the full episode: https://l.prageru.com/3NATPQw
